snippet.title: Death Ray Manta SE: Official Steam Trailer (Windows)
snippet.description:
Death Ray Manta is a game by Rob Fearon and Andy White with music by Mike Daw. (re)Launching onto Windows in mid September 2015.

It has colours and lasers and lasers and colours and oh my.

http://www.futureofvideogames.co.uk
